eplicated by the monsters. For more flags you collect, more enemies will show on the map!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/d6238c674e8b61a6fbf22076c5825240.poster.avif?t=1670644457\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/d6238c674e8b61a6fbf22076c5825240.webm?t=1670644457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/d6238c674e8b61a6fbf22076c5825240.mp4?t=1670644457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It can't be a Halloween game without costumes! Collect all the candies to unlock many costumes to use in your adventure! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/79a1411acc1bf4fe396b3a3e1ad51228.poster.avif?t=1670644457\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/79a1411acc1bf4fe396b3a3e1ad51228.webm?t=1670644457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/79a1411acc1bf4fe396b3a3e1ad51228.mp4?t=1670644457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>So you beat the stages on campaign? Time to reach that right score! On Endless Mode you can choose your favorite stage and try to collect many flags as possible!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/467d4113e62ef708ca4fb9cd2b4ac40d.poster.avif?t=1670644457\" width=616 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/467d4113e62ef708ca4fb9cd2b4ac40d.webm?t=1670644457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/467d4113e62ef708ca4fb9cd2b4ac40d.mp4?t=1670644457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>How about play with your friends in a total chaotic game mode? On Multiplayer you can play up to 4 players Local and see who survives at the end!<br><br><br>Get the flags, run for your life... And from yourself!<br><br>You are a blissful child taking part in a capture the flag championship in exchange for treats, until something terrifying starts to happen...<br><br>No matter how much you run, monsters chase after you mimicking your every move!<br><br>Grab the flags, escape the monsters and find out what's behind this great mystery!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286670/extras/99f90041acf51daa7418cb5a9463e301.avif?t=1670644457\" width=616 height=66 /></span>",
